dmv.spring.demo.model.repository

Class JdbcConnector

  • java.lang.Object
    • dmv.spring.demo.model.repository.JdbcConnector
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.AutoCloseable

    public class JdbcConnector
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.AutoCloseable
    Custom made manager for Connection and PreparedStatement, to be used in Repository classes. Reducing boilerplate code.

    SQLException will be converted to AccessDataBaseException at this level: opening and closing connections, setting parameters.

    It's not thread safe, and expected to be created and then closed within a single method.

    Author:
    dmv
